</div>
<div>
<p>初<pc>，</pc>
<persName>劉平</persName>
<pc>、</pc>
<persName>石元孫</persName>被執<pc>，</pc>
<name key="盧守勤" type="givenName">守勤</name>撫膺涕泣不敢出<pc>，</pc>又嚐易蕃官馬<pc>。</pc>
