<pc>，</pc>雍欲遣安撫<term>都監</term>李康伯往說賊<pc>，</pc>不肯行<pc>，</pc>賊去而<name key="盧守勤" type="givenName">守勤</name>
<pc>、</pc>用章更相論奏<pc>。</pc>知製誥葉清臣以<name key="盧守勤" type="givenName">守勤</name>擁兵觀望<pc>，</pc>請正其罪<pc>，</pc>並按<measure quantity="2" unit="people">
<num value="2">二</num>人</measure>
<pc>。</pc>
<name key="盧守勤" type="givenName">守勤</name>奪<term>防禦使</term>
<pc>，</pc>為湖北<term>都監</term>
<pc>；</pc>用章除籍<pc>，</pc>配<placeName>雷州</placeName>本城<pc>；</pc>康伯<pc>，</pc>均州<term>都監</term>
